snippet.title: Water Delivery - Official Trailer | Ghouls 4 Games
snippet.description: Watch the unsettling trailer for Water Delivery, an upcoming first-person, horror experience where you play as a water delivery boy. Ride along in the delivery truck from house to house. Deliver filled water jugs, find and return empty jugs, and collect all the payments. Will you be able to finish your final route of the evening? Water Delivery will be available on PC.
